These are Puzzles for 3x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-1::.
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: lily, aconite
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: skiing, water-polo
The people use 2 different means of transport: roller, taxi
1. the person who's sport is skiing is on the right of the person driving the roller##1
2. the person who growsaconite is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |
| Flower   | aconite    | lily |
| Sport         | water-polo | skiing    |
| Transport     | roller     | taxi      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: mirinda, sprite
There 2 different types of food: lime, watermelon
The people use 2 different means of transport: motorbike, train
1. the person driving the train is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
2. the person eating lime is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |
| Beverage      | sprite  | mirinda   |
| Food   | watermelon | lime  |
| Transport     | train   | motorbike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-3::.
2 different games are played: canasta, go
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: fantasy, martial-arts
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: ice-hockey, swimming
1. the person playing go is in an even position##4
2. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |
| Game         | canasta   | go  |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts | fantasy  |
| Sport         | ice-hockey   | swimming |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-4::.
