.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-15::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: collecting, rock-climbing
There are 2 different nationalities: colombian, indian
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: disco, folk
1. the fan of folk is on the left of the fan of disco##1
2. the colombian is on the left of the indian##1
3. the person who's hobby is collecting is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |
| Hobby         | rock-climbing | collecting |
| Nationality   | colombian     | indian     |
| Music-Genre           | folk          | disco     |

